                <expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uintus</ex></expan> Octavius <expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uinti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibertus</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Reutus <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Scaefius <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>ai</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibertus</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>Seleucus <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> Vibius <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>uci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibertus</ex></expan> Stabilio <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> Vibius Chres<expan><ex>t</ex><abbr>us</abbr></expan> <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> Gavius <expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>iti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibertus</ex></expan> Hilari<supplied reason="lost">o</supplied> <lb n="8"/>viocuri in viam <lb n="9"/>silice sternend<supplied reason="lost">am</supplied><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="10"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>NV<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="0"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Fundumstände des Steins unbekannt. 1. Beleg für Existenz eines collegium von viocuri in einem municipium. Die nomina gentilia sind in der Gegend bereits bezeugt. (B): Z. 1-7: falsche Lesung der Namen. Z. 10: [---]NV GEMIN[---]- v. Wonterghem, AE; anhand Foto nicht zu entscheiden.</p>
